creator: Team RH Fitness Ltd
descriptionHtml:
So we know the key to fat loss is being a caloric deficit yeah? The problem is, everyone is different shapes and sizes, along with different activity levels. There for everyone's calories for fat loss is different.

Well at TeamRH we've analysed and correlated over 25,000+ user data and come up with our own advanced calorie guide for fat loss. So now you simply pop in your individual stats and activity, and we work out your exact calories for fat loss. 100% guaranteed results.

So what else does the app have to offer ?

Well we can claim to be one of the very small amount of companies out there who have the privilege of teaming up with "myfitnespal" which is a fantastic calorie counting app. This enables us to see your data 24/7 so we can always offer you guidance should things need tweaking.

Within the app we will set your goals to achieve each day, where you can earn gold stars, and medals. We believe this is a fantastic way to keep you accountable, and something to always focus on!

There is a video library where you can find an absolute plethora of content on nutrition and exercise, told in our very own no bs manor.

A news feed section so you can keep up to date on the latest news with TEAMRH - we like to keep you guys up to date with the latest info fresh off the press!

We also have an amazing exercise guide, where we choose a program we feel is best suited to your body weight and fitness levels.

If you want to lose fat, the right way, no more shakes, no more pills, then all we ask you is put your trust into us and we will change your life forever

Love
Richie & Rach
Your coaches at TEAMRH
descriptionShort: Want to lose fat? Look no further than TeamRH <3

title: Team RH Fitness

creator: Team RH Fitness Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Take back control with Team RH: the no BS health plan which promotes sustainable weight loss, realistic goals and no banned food.
WHAT MAKES TEAM RH UNIQUE?

No banned foods - We don’t stop you or your family eating your favourite food. Instead, we help you manage macros to maintain a calorie deficit.
Realistic goals - Team RH set realistic, personalised calorie, protein, fibre, workout and step goals, so you’ll lose weight without going hungry.

Nutritional advice - Our focus on nutrition rather than quick fixes or banning foods teaches you healthy habits that’ll last for life.

100% honesty - No pills, no shakes, no BS. We know these lose fat quick fixes don’t work, with 83% of Team RH members joining us after failing on other weight loss plans.

Optional Workouts - The Team RH app provides a library of workout videos & tutorials for you to choose from.

WHAT DO YOU DO AS A TEAM RH MEMBER?
Visualise your progress - visualise progress on your personalised dashboard that’s more than just a calorie counter. Alongside calories, track protein, fibre, water, weight and workouts.
Reach fitness goals and lose fat - Team RH has teamed up with MyFitnessPal Calorie Counter, so that you can easily input your meals to hit the realistic calorie goals Team RH set you.
Access quick and easy recipes - Our recipe section has hundreds of simple to follow, healthy recipes that list the macros of each dish, so you can track your macros easily.
Learn healthy habits - Team RH’s help centre teaches priceless health lessons that last for life, through informative articles, recommendations, and quick fitness tips and tricks.
Get fit and stay fit - Team RH provides an optional structured workout plan personalised to your get fit needs. We also have a whole library of workout video guides, should you want to mix it up a little.
descriptionShort: Want to lose fat? Look no further than TeamRH <3
